The 93rd edition of the Comrades Marathon is taking place in KwaZulu-Natal where thousands of runners from around the world make the 90km run from Pietermaritzburg to the Moses Mabhida Stadium in Durban. JOHANNESBURG - The 93rd edition of the Comrades Marathon is taking place in KwaZulu-Natal where thousands of runners from around the world make the 90km run from Pietermaritzburg to the Moses Mabhida Stadium in Durban.  See the race's route map, here and track the live leaderboard on the Comrades website.